
Ingredients for 4:
* 400 gr. spaghetti
* 200 gr. pecorino cheese
* black pepper
* oil
* salt

Directions:
Put a pot of salted water on to boil.
In a large bowl, combine the cheeses and
black pepper; mash with just enough cold
water to make a thick paste.
Spread the paste evenly in the bowl.
Once the water is boiling, add the pasta.
Stir vigorously to coat the pasta.
